<br>
These changes are good. They show VI is thinking about how to fix some of the MAJOR problems/issues with this game and issues that will come up in PoP (I'm amazed they are actually doing this NOW instead of 6 months after PoP has ruined other encounters). We can worry about the actual changes, and they may reverse/alter some of these changes, and will definitely add more, but abject *whining* about it is worthless and the complaints show how completely out of whack some people's view of this game is.<br>
<br>
So yes, as the subject title of this thread says, I say &quot;WTG VI&quot;. You are actually listening to the players and trying to get the game more balanced.<br>
